*eventmachine-1.0.8 (07 Aug 2015)

  07 Aug 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +eventmachine-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  05 Jul 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> eventmachine-1.0.7.ebuild:
  ...and also add the slot to the built-time dependency of openssl.

  05 Jul 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> eventmachine-1.0.7.ebuild:
  Fix openssl slot to be the one that can be compiled against.

  05 Jul 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> eventmachine-1.0.7.ebuild:
  Avoid tests requiring a network connection, fixing bug 342029. Fix openssl
  slot dependency.

*eventmachine-1.0.7 (10 Jun 2015)

  10 Jun 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +eventmachine-1.0.7.ebuild:
