  Stable for x86, wrt bug #551420

  08 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> eventmachine-1.0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #551420

*eventmachine-1.0.3-r2 (07 Jun 2015)

